A ''neighbourhood structure'' $$\mathcal{N}$$ on a set $$X$$ is an assignment to each $$x \in X$$ of a [[filter|Filter (Topology)]] $$\mathcal{N}(x)$$ on $$X$$ all of whose elements contain the point $$x$$.